22#ifndef GCC_LRA_H
23#define GCC_LRA_H
24
25extern bool lra_simple_p;
26
27/* Return the allocno reg class of REGNO. If it is a reload pseudo,
28 the pseudo should finally get hard register of the allocno
29 class. */
30static inline enum reg_class
31lra_get_allocno_class (int regno)
32{
33 resize_reg_info ();
34 return reg_allocno_class (regno);
35}
36
37extern rtx lra_create_new_reg (machine_mode, rtx, enum reg_class,
38 const char *);
39extern rtx lra_eliminate_regs (rtx, machine_mode, rtx);
40extern void lra (FILE *);
41extern void lra_init_once (void);
42extern void lra_finish_once (void);
43
44#endif /* GCC_LRA_H */
